ZH: 这个间谍已经在这个国家潜伏了很久。
EN: This spy has been lurking in this country for a long time.

ZH: 他们的真实身份潜伏在那个小村庄里。
EN: Their true identities are lurking in that small village.

ZH: 这个病毒可能在人体内潜伏多年而不被察觉。
EN: This virus may lurk in the human body for years without being detected.

ZH: 据说这座城市的地下有一支恐怖分子组织在潜伏。
EN: It is said that an underground terrorist organization is lurking in this city.

ZH: 他以普通市民的身份潜伏在政府机关中，获取情报。
EN: He lurks in government agencies as an ordinary civilian to obtain intelligence.

ZH: 犯罪分子潜伏在人群中，等待着时机行动。
EN: The criminals lurk in the crowd, waiting for the right moment to act.

ZH: 这个毒贩一直在边境地区潜伏，继续走私毒品。
EN: The drug trafficker has been lurking in the border area, continuing to smuggle drugs.

ZH: 潜伏在暗处的恶势力时刻准备着对社会造成破坏。
EN: The evil forces lurking in the shadows are always ready to cause damage to society.

ZH: 黑客通过潜伏在系统中的后门获取了用户的个人信息。
EN: The hacker obtained users' personal information by lurking in the system's backdoor.

ZH: 恶势力已经在这个城市潜伏多年，导致治安问题日益严峻。
EN: The evil forces have been lurking in this city for many years, resulting in increasingly severe public security issues.

ZH: 警方已经派出特工潜伏在危险分子中，以便于及时抓捕。
EN: The police have dispatched undercover agents to lurk among the dangerous individuals for timely arrests.

ZH: 这个间谍潜伏在敌对势力内部，为我方提供重要情报。
EN: This spy lurks within the hostile forces and provides vital intelligence for us.

ZH: 隐形敌机成功地潜伏在敌对领空进行侦察任务。
EN: The stealth fighter successfully lurked in enemy territory for reconnaissance missions.

